                    <h2> What am i doing with my life?</h2>
                    <p> If you are too young to question that to yourself, please don't read further. It's embarassing to me trying to explain something that only someone passing through a existencial crisis can feel. Its like explaining hemorroids to someone
                        that never had. This website is part of the superation of a dificult fase of a human being that is inexorable to all of us. You will suffer from this, sooner or later!</p>
                    <h2> I developed this website in my thirties! </h2>
                        <p> I believe that the age mentioned is self explaining. It's like saying that i have 15 years old and am in my puberty. If you say that is in your thirties there is no denying that you have a existencial crisis in progress. Don't deny it,
                            this only make the things worse!</p>
        
                    <h1>So what is your purpose? Trow it!</h1>
